MEDIA COLLABORATIONPROFESSIONAL AUDIONEW! CONVERGE Pro 2NEW! CONVERGE PA AmpsNEW! CONVERGE Pro 2 Touch-Panel ControllerNEW! CONVERGE Pro 2 DialerNEW! CONVERGE Pro 2 ExpandersCONVERGE MatrixCONVERGE ProCONVERGE Pro 880CONVERGE Pro 880TCONVERGE Pro 880TACONVERGE Pro 840TCONVERGE Pro 8iCONVERGE Pro TH20CONVERGE Pro VH20CONVERGE ConsoleCONVERGE SRCONVERGE USBINTERACT ProCONNECT Network BridgesAccessoriesTabletop ControllerSABINE BrandNETWORK MEDIA STREAMINGRESIDENTIAL STREAMINGUC VOICEDIGITAL SIGNAGEMICROPHONESMEDIA CARTSpromotionsWhere to Buy


CONVERGE® Pro

	The CONVERGE Pro series of next-generation professional audio conferencing products delivers a new level of unrivaled performance, flexibility, and manageability.







NEW! CONVERGE® Pro 2

					CONVERGE Pro 2 is the industry’s most advanced professional audio DSP platform for conferencing and sound reinforcement applications.

- Learn More












CONVERGE Pro 880

					The successor to the industry-leading XAP 800. As the flagship product in ClearOne’s next-generation Converge Pro professional audio conferencing product line, the 880 is a complete audio system that delivers rich functionality with improved audio performance, enhanced management, and simplified configuration for audio conferencing.

- Learn More







					 

CONVERGE Pro 880T

					Combine the rich functionality of the CONVERGE Pro 880 with a built-in telephone interface and speaker amplifier.

- Learn More











									 

CONVERGE Pro 880TA

									A complete conferencing solution with four power amplifiers delivering enhanced management features, simplified configuration tools and industry-leading expandability for use in virtually any venue and application.

- Learn More











					 

CONVERGE Pro 840T

					The CONVERGE Pro 840T combines the features of the Converge Pro 800 with a single-line telephone interface and a 10-watt amplifier for stand-alone conferencing applications.

- Learn More







					 

CONVERGE Pro 8i

					New input only platform adds eight more inputs to CONVERGE Pro system at a lower price, allowing customers to match the number of inputs and outputs required.

- Learn More







					 

CONVERGE Pro TH20

					The CONVERGE Pro TH20 adds telephone conferencing capabilities to the CONVERGE Pro 880. It also adds two additional line inputs and outputs.

- Learn More







					 

CONVERGE Pro VH20

					A VoIP endpoint enables the CONVERGE Pro system to directly connect to a VoIP PBX. The VH20 uses a SIP-based protocol that is interoperable with major PBX manufacturers including Cisco, Avaya and others.

- Learn More





	 


 
  


